{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_0187iNBGDmvDtwHQMeQMFDB6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All three members are healthy:\n\n- **mongodb-replica-0**: PRIMARY (health=1), Ready 1/1\n- **mongodb-replica-1**: SECONDARY (health=1), Ready 1/1  \n- **mongodb-replica-2**: SECONDARY (health=1), Ready 1/1\n\n**Root cause:** The `health-overrides` ConfigMap had an incorrect/stale password entry (`legacyHealthPass123`) for `mongodb-replica-1`. The health check script reads pod-name-keyed overrides and used this wrong password instead of the correct `healthpass123` from the `health-user-password` secret, causing authentication failures on every readiness probe.\n\n**Fix applied:** Removed the incorrect `mongodb-replica-1` key from the `health-overrides` ConfigMap. Once the ConfigMap propagated to the pod (~1 minute), the next liveness probe failure triggered a container restart. After restart, the health check used the correct password from the secret and both probes passed, restoring the pod to Ready state."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":744,"cache_read_input_tokens":38167,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":744},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2a5620da-e5c3-4a05-bcca-a0ca75bdc4ff","uuid":"68526b21-2a90-4771-8948-ad6accda7bed","request_id":"req_011CcQG4v1GwEqaBXveMGrvy"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":238764,"duration_api_ms":101542,"ttft_ms":3213,"ttft_stream_ms":1973,"time_to_request_ms":330,"num_turns":20,"result":"All three members are healthy:\n\n- **mongodb-replica-0**: PRIMARY (health=1), Ready 1/1\n- **mongodb-replica-1**: SECONDARY (health=1), Ready 1/1  \n- **mongodb-replica-2**: SECONDARY (health=1), Ready 1/1\n\n**Root cause:** The `health-overrides` ConfigMap had an incorrect/stale password entry (`legacyHealthPass123`) for `mongodb-replica-1`. The health check script reads pod-name-keyed overrides and used this wrong password instead of the correct `healthpass123` from the `health-user-password` secret, causing authentication failures on every readiness probe.\n\n**Fix applied:** Removed the incorrect `mongodb-replica-1` key from the `health-overrides` ConfigMap. Once the ConfigMap propagated to the pod (~1 minute), the next liveness probe failure triggered a container restart. After restart, the health check used the correct password from the secret and both probes passed, restoring the pod to Ready state.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"2a5620da-e5c3-4a05-bcca-a0ca75bdc4ff","total_cost_usd":0.4006162,"usage":{"input_tokens":22,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21961,"cache_read_input_tokens":649674,"output_tokens":4877,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":21961,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":237,"cache_read_input_tokens":38167,"cache_creation_input_tokens":744,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":744},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":647,"outputTokens":16,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.000727,"contextWindow":200000,"ma